c: 3
v: 167
t: "And so He may test the hypocrites! They were told, \"Come, fight in the path of Allah, or (at least) defend (yourself against the enemy).\" But they responded, \"We would have followed you, if we had known (for sure) that there would be a battle.\" That day, they were nearer apostasy than belief. By their lips, they were declaring that which (just) wasn´t there in their hearts. Allah is well Aware of what they conceal"